    "body": "To be more specific, are there any future plans for Cython to be used for generic use, apart from the standard behavior of generating C extensions for CPython?\r\n\r\nI would like to use Cython the same way is used for CPython, but for standard shared libraries or monolithic binaries.\r\n\r\nI find it very easy to express myself in Cython and stay the least 99% concentrated than in any other language I have used so far.\r\n\r\nHas anyone asked a similar question like this in the past?",
